title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Airbus H135 - version 1.4.3
description:
The Airbus H135  has been recently update to version 1.4.3 and now has a high skids edition which makes the quality of this helicopter even higher than it already was. We start by looking at the exterior following by the cockpit and after that will take the helicopter out for a short flight.

The latest version of the helicopter can be downloaded from flightsim.to:
https://flightsim.to/file/8970/airbus-h135-helicopter-project
